message: Rudy should be a poet. He truely has a way with words. He also cleaned up NYC when no other politicians cared. Regrettably though, it has become over crowded & way over commercialize. It's commonly called gentrification. That's like when a waitress at Cheesecake Factory, can't afford to dine at Morton's Steak House on her day off, on a whim or craving. Planet Hollywood six blocks from Hard Rock Cafe & both successfully doing business? Over crowded & over gentrified.
